title: Flight Simulator 2020 - Addon spotlight - Airbus H135 Helicopter v1.1
description:
In this video we will look at version 1.1 of the Airbus H135 Helicopter. With this release the HPG development group releases a stable version of the helicopter. Although the development releases were already very stable as well. In this 1.1 release several enhancements have been made and some polishing has been done to make the helicopter even nicer. 

If you also want to give the helicopter a try you can download it from the site below:
https://flightsim.to/file/8970/airbus-h135-helicopter-project
